model

类 Optionset

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Optionset
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Optionset
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Each car has several option sets, such as car color, car transmission selection and so on. For each option set, there is a lot of options and for each option, there is a name and a price. So in order to establish a car configuration model, not only car option set should be considered, but options selection also should be. Two classes are included in this .java file. Optionset class is the outter class and Option class is the inner class of Optionset, which contains its option name and its option price.

    Also in order to keep our option set data and option data from corruption, serialization can be very helpful. So Serizalizable interface is implemented both in Optionset class and Option class.
